question: Will another candidate win the VA-5 Republican House Primary?
description:
This market will resolve to “Yes” if any candidate other than Bob Good or John McGuire wins the 2024 Republican Primary for the 5th Virginia Congressional District (VA-5). Otherwise, this market will resolve to “No”.

If no 2024 Republican Primary for the 5th Virginia Congressional District (VA-5) takes place this market will resolve to “Yes”. 

The resolution source for this market will be the first announcement of the results from the Virginia Republican Primary, however an overwhelming consensus of credible reporting may suffice.

question: Euro 2024: Favorite fails to advance beyond group stage?
description:
If any one of the listed teams below does NOT advance from the Group Stage of EURO 2024, this market will resolve to "Yes": France, England, Germany, Netherlands, Spain, Portugal, Belgium, or Italy. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

Note, all listed teams must advance from the Group Stage in order to resolve this market to "No". If at least one of the listed teams does not advance from the Group Stage, this market will resolve to "Yes".

If at any point it is impossible for one of the listed teams to advance from the Group Stage according to the rules of the tournament, this market will immediately resolve to "Yes". Likewise, if it can at any point be definitively determined that all of the listed teams will advance from the Group Stage, this market will immediately resolve to "No".

events.title: Euro 2024: Favorite fails to advance beyond group stage?
